  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104510/extras/f8bfc7867ebe4b4d8ed7932107837b6b.avif?t=1758020421\" width=616 height=76 /></span><br><br>Adorable city builder set in the same rabbit universe as Farm Keeper.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Build and Expand Your Cute Rabbit Town</h2>Create a bustling community where every resident is a lovable bunny. Watch your town grow as more rabbits hop in to help you expand. Enjoy the adorable pixel art style that brings your rabbit town to life.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104510/extras/7ebdd88e30ecdbad3fd9565f718514b4.poster.avif?t=1758020421\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104510/extras/7ebdd88e30ecdbad3fd9565f718514b4.webm?t=1758020421\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104510/extras/7ebdd88e30ecdbad3fd9565f718514b4.mp4?t=1758020421\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Defend or Conquer</h2>Train a fluffy army to protect your town or raid empire locations. Witness exciting battles as your rabbit warriors fight for your cause. Prefer a peaceful experience? Enjoy the game's relaxing peaceful mode.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104510/extras/bafc80b5a06add52a676e07cdea1243e.poster.avif?t=1758020421\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104510/extras/bafc80b5a06add52a676e07cdea1243e.webm?t=1758020421\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104510/extras/bafc80b5a06add52a676e07cdea1243e.mp4?t=1758020421\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Master Building Combos</h2>Discover unique adjacent bonuses for each building. Experiment with different combinations to maximize efficiency. Adapt your strategy to randomly generated maps for endless replayability.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104510/extras/0191e607b3f557a98b96d7295d613661.poster.avif?t=1758020421\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104510/extras/0191e607b3f557a98b96d7295d613661.webm?t=1758020421\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104510/extras/0191e607b3f557a98b96d7295d613661.mp4?t=1758020421\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unlock New Ways to Play</h2>Make meaningful choices in building selection, upgrades, trade, and research. Discover new strategies as you progress and succeed. Unlock exciting content including new town types, unique townhalls, bonus perks, and challenging difficulty levels<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104510/extras/2f35866b80dd73da0162e77f29b151b6.poster.avif?t=1758020421\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104510/extras/2f35866b80dd73da0162e77f29b151b6.webm?t=1758020421\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104510/extras/2f35866b80dd73da0162e77f29b151b6.mp4?t=1758020421\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
