afc80b5a06add52a676e07cdea1243e.mp4?t=1758020421\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Master Building Combos</h2>Discover unique adjacent bonuses for each building. Experiment with different combinations to maximize efficiency. Adapt your strategy to randomly generated maps for endless replayability.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104510/extras/0191e607b3f557a98b96d7295d613661.poster.avif?t=1758020421\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104510/extras/0191e607b3f557a98b96d7295d613661.webm?t=1758020421\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104510/extras/0191e607b3f557a98b96d7295d613661.mp4?t=1758020421\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unlock New Ways to Play</h2>Make meaningful choices in building selection, upgrades, trade, and research. Discover new strategies as you progress and succeed. Unlock exciting content including new town types, unique townhalls, bonus perks, and challenging difficulty levels<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104510/extras/2f35866b80dd73da0162e77f29b151b6.poster.avif?t=1758020421\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104510/extras/2f35866b80dd73da0162e77f29b151b6.webm?t=1758020421\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3104510/extras/2f35866b80dd73da0162e77f29b151b6.mp4?t=1758020421\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
